- option to enable debug (--debug or --verbose or -d)
- option to force output dir (--output-dir or -o <output dir>)
- option to exit or not on failure (--exit-on-failure or -e)
- Multi browser support
- Force browser arg (--browser or -b <browser>)
- Make repo public (protect branches, rules, etc..)
- Add the possibility to export messages (by using the --messages or -m option)